{"tid":1975661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 五一黃圈週 文宣組 黃店老闆 員工 所有手足入","createTime":"2020-04-16T16:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T09:00:01.000Z","uid":11870,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1a94cf083f91eca518458cdb2a8fb9806b7e14","tid":1975661,"uid":11870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"原post: [五一黃金週] 係時候包裝到同抗爭有關睇你支那夠唔夠膽放自由行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1960318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1960318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想要文宣手足 幫幫手<br />\n如果你係黃店老闆或者員工都想你幫手<br />\n<br />\n我地要將五一包裝成為香港既節日<br />\n如果港共想係五月前通返關 阻止唔到 我地就同佢做輸出革命 <br />\n<br />\n你幻想下 Sogo月尾又thankful 再通關 成個尖沙咀 銅鑼灣會有幾撚多蟈人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係時候做野喇各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09181e7c0d9e6b1abc46705f292817a122d32bab","tid":1975661,"uid":11870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaiuyBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaiuyBj.jpg&h=698afba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngkwMWo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngkwMWo.png&h=e68027a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c16cbde2fa06c5f87925c8cc25bea11af2a6a8","tid":1975661,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"借個位唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩黃店老闆們同最近對黃圈覺得灰心嘅你入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1975615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1975615</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ccbfe51c732efa7e64669d8614fc61925bdf5c1","tid":1975661,"uid":11870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:42:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"